# Exercises index file

Do **not** create, recreate, update, or “fix” **`core-exercises/cursor-training-exercises-index.md`**. That path is intentionally absent from this repo.

When exercise order or links are needed, refer to the **`exercise-N/`** folders and their markdown files under `core-exercises/` directly. Do not replace this with a new index file of the same role unless the user explicitly asks for a differently named file.
